## 5. Pipeline Flow (What Runs When)

### Daily Premarket (Mon–Fri 07:00 → 09:35)
```
07:00  catalyst_analysis.py
       └─ Fetches earnings, news, K4 kill switches

07:30  finviz_screener_agent.py (Phase 3)
       ├─ Runs 19 custom screeners
       ├─ Institutional discovery (independent of VIF)
       └─ Outputs JSON to reports/catalysts/
       
08:45  orchestrator.py --mode premarket
       ├─ catalyst_analysis.py (fresh run, populates K4)
       ├─ watchlist_watcher.py --all --period 1mo (VIF signals, 1-month data)
       └─ swing_trade_screener_v2.py (5 setup types)
       └─ Generates combined HTML report
```

### Daily Market Hours (Mon–Fri 09:35)
```
09:35  orchestrator.py --mode market_open
       ├─ swing_trade_screener_v2.py (updated screens)
       └─ HTML report
```

### After Hours (Mon–Fri 16:05)
```
16:05  orchestrator.py --mode afterhours
       ├─ daily_watchlist_analysis.py (conviction model)
       ├─ watchlist_watcher.py --all --period 5d (VIF signals, 5-day data)
       └─ HTML report
```

### End of Week (Friday 16:30)
```
16:30  orchestrator.py --mode full
       └─ All of the above (premarket + market_open + afterhours)
```

### Weekend (Sat 08:00 + Sun 18:00)
```
Sat 08:00 & Sun 18:00  orchestrator.py --mode weekend
       ├─ weekend_catalyst_agent.py (Monday morning briefing)
       └─ HTML report with macro analysis
```

